snippet.title: Quake 3 Arena: Trailer (a video game)
snippet.description: Rated M for mature by the "Entertainment Software Rating Board" [ESRB]. For PC (computer video game from 1999). First Person Shooter. @ID software and the players: The videogame edition "Ultimate Quake" with together Quake 1,2,3 on 3 CDs there is Quake 3Arena damaged and it makes a damage to the computer. You can hear a bad noise coming out of the computer :-( !: Please fix that and to the players: Get the old package of "Quake 3 Arena" from the year 1999! I think there was a clean videogame version.
